Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.61,0:01:41.38,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}就算绕了些远
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.64,0:01:43.96,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}这份思念
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.31,0:01:49.32,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}也想直接亲口告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.06,0:01:52.28,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}总会有一日
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.10,0:01:55.98,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}飞向蓝天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.30,0:02:01.27,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}属于我的蓝色天使啊{\fnMS Gothic}…
